{"tid":330832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港啲垃圾體育評術員","createTime":"2017-07-21T14:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T09:16:52.000Z","uid":38928,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"bfed893026aaf6e009efc96d3f83f7787d1b62c8","tid":330832,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"次次聽到都燥，句句都廢話<br />\n1.最興叫到爆咪「嘩勁呀！」「好呀！」「好嘢！」「好難得」<br />\n2.一係讀啲球員資料<br />\n3.一係講啲獎門人式嘅嘢：「好佩服日本隊嘅鬥志，不過中國隊都好勁呀」<br />\n4.空泛，言之無物：「我覺得呢個球員防守真係差啲呀」、「係呀，其他方面都幾好，係呢度做得唔夠好」咁姐係防守嘅邊方面、咩技術做得唔好？<br />\n<br />\n記得之前睇過段麻雀旁述，雖然講蝗語，但個評述員分析戰略同具體咁講到佢地咁打有咩利弊，聽完會令知個形勢係點，唔係一味叫同講廢話zip時間"},{"pid":"31da87dfabc273b329d9a2b0708fae76f78557d6","tid":330832,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"雷sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f20cda96916f0a1560634ea164ed6182773d97","tid":330832,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雷sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩！<br />\n黎喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7befb31c9696b5f4028c6887acfcd3055922913a","tid":330832,"uid":124667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯 果d入波靜係識叫 goal,........................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................